HEADWORD: Edifier
<hw>Ed"i*fi`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
builds.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who edifies, builds up, or strengthens another
by moral or religious instruction.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Edify</ent>⟦br⟧
